### Create booking
POST http://localhost:8080/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "submitdate": "2026-05-08T15:00:00",
  "customerid": 1,
  "roomid": 2,
  "bedcount": 2,
  "nightcount": 3,
  "startdate": "2026-06-01",
  "enddate": "2026-06-04",
  "cost": 4500
}

### Get all bookings
GET http://localhost:8080/bookings